You probably need to increase the amount of RAM available to your JVM.  

See the parameters:
-Xmx   :Maximum memory usable by the JVM
-Xms   :Initial memory allocated to JVM

My params are;  -Xmx2048m -Xms128m  (2G max, 128M initial)


