On Dec 10, 2004, at 4:16 PM, Ravi wrote:
>  If I close a MultiSearcher, does it close all the associated searchers
> too?

It sure does:

   public void close() throws IOException {
     for (int i = 0; i < searchables.length; i++)
       searchables[i].close();
   }


