> 1.0 = tf(termFreq(contents:ibm)=1)
> 
> 0.7768564 = idf(docFreq=4)
> 
> 0.09375 = fieldNorm(field=contents, doc=2)
> 
> 0.038040176 = weight(contents:risc in 2), product of:
> 
