I have a version 'UnicodeData.txt' here.
It lists ~ 12000 characters in the form
01A4;LATIN CAPITAL LETTER P WITH HOOK;Lu;0;L;;;;;N;LATIN CAPITAL LETTER P HOOK;;;01A5;
